On-Premises Information System Architecture = Cloud Architecture

	Worklod (More emphasize in Cloud)
	Services (More emphasize in Cloud)
	Virtual Machine (More emphasize in Cloud)
	Management Plane (Only in Cloud)
	Virtualization: Platform, Maitenance and Licensing
	Pyhisical Infraestucture:Power, Network, Storage and Racks
	Pyhisical Facility: Costs of Sapace, Physical Security and Personnel

Types of Cloud Services
	Workload: SaaS.  (Easier administration)
	Services: PaaS
	Virtual Machine: IaaS. (Easier control)

Accesing Cloud Services
	The most important thing that we would be connet to the cloud is the use of internet.
	We can use to different ways to connect: Tunneling (vpn) or Endpoint
	Security is provider by vendor, using 3 security components CIA

Why I love the Cloud